title: ArchetypeSC.com Website
desc: ArchetypeSC website was outdated and no longer highlighted core company services. New website design was created and brought to life to better illustrate these values as well as creating a new, modern design to better represent the company and help it stand out amongst competitors. This design was created and re ned with guidance from high level executives to be sure the company was represented accurately. Tools used were Sketch and Adobe Illustrator.
